				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div role="note" class="hatnote">This article is about a form of discrimination. For other uses of the word, see <a href="/wiki/Mentalism_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Mentalism (disambiguation)">mentalism (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
